 ğŸ“œ 3. S3 Bucket Policy

 âœ… Definition

Bucket Policy ek resource-based policy hoti hai jo directly S3 bucket par apply hoti hai aur JSON format me likhi jaati hai.

---

 ğŸ”¹ Important Policy Elements

 Effect â†’ Allow / Deny
 Principal â†’ Kaun access karega
 Action â†’ Kya access milega
 Resource â†’ Kis bucket/object par

---

 ğŸ“„ 4. JSON Policy (Basics + Code Understanding)

 âœ… What is JSON?

JSON (JavaScript Object Notation) ek lightweight data format hai jo data ko keyâ€“value pairs me represent karta hai.

ğŸ‘‰ AWS me saari policies JSON format me hoti hain.

---

 ğŸ”¹ Sample S3 Bucket Policy (Public Read)

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": "",
      "Action": "s3:GetObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::example-bucket/"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

 ğŸ§  Code Explanation

 Version â†’ Policy language version
 Statement â†’ Rules ka set
 Effect â†’ Allow access
 Principal â†’ Sab users
 Action â†’ File read kar sakte hain
 Resource â†’ Bucket ke objects

