 ğŸ› ï¸ 5. AWS Policy Generator

 âœ… What is AWS Policy Generator?

AWS Policy Generator ek online AWS tool hai jo JSON policies automatically generate karta hai.

ğŸ‘‰ Beginners ke liye bahut useful hai.

---

 ğŸ”¹ How You Used AWS Policy Generator

1. Open AWS Policy Generator
2. Select policy type â†’ S3 Bucket Policy
3. Choose Effect â†’ Allow
4. Select Action â†’ `s3:GetObject`
5. Enter Bucket ARN
6. Add Statement
7. Generate Policy

