 ğŸš« 6. Real Problem Faced & Solution

 âŒ Problem

 S3 bucket me uploaded file open nahi ho rahi thi
 URL ke through access blocked tha

ğŸ‘‰ Reason: Bucket permissions block thi

---

 âœ… Solution

