 ğŸŒ 7. URL Access via Policy

 âœ… Learning

 S3 object ko URL se access karne ke liye:

   Bucket policy allow honi chahiye
   `s3:GetObject` permission required hoti hai

ğŸ‘‰ Sirf file upload karna kaafi nahi hota, policy bhi chahiye hoti hai.

